<C>__{dr. ambrose}
<D>__{alrighty. let's get started folks.}
<A>__{reverse on two other doctors who are busying themselves collecting instrument. allison and sage. they walk over to trevor's body and get to work. sage sticks a needle in trevor's arm.}
