<D>__{collecting 40ccs of serum...}
<C>__{ambrose}
<D>__{examining cranial fracture...}
<A>__{allison at his side, ambrose checks the wound on trevor's head, pauses to look inside trevor's eyes. trevor's pov: ambrose closing the eyelid again.}
