<D>__{checking oral cavity for blockage...}
<A>__{ambrose opens trevor's mouth.}
<C>__{ambrose }
<D>__{and we have a winner...}
<A>__{ambrose pulls a long black dead lamprey out of trevor's mouth. looks at the slippery creature for a moment.}
